eated":1639199888,"deleted":0,"content":"以前一直不明白，电视 /机顶盒厂商把 USB3.0 阉割成 2.0 ，千兆 LAN 阉割成百兆，能省几个钱。\r\n结果今天在雷鸟的论坛看到，其产品的 Wifi6 都仅支持 200Mbps ，有用户提到是联发科芯片的原因。\r\n遂前往联发科官网查询，发现如下：\r\n[MT9632]( https://www.mediatek.cn/products/productSpecs/mt9632)\r\n\r\nhttps://loli.tc/image/Qtyv\r\n\r\n仅 USB2.0 ，并因此导致走 usb 的网卡也仅能跑满 2.0 的速度。\r\n不明白所谓旗舰芯片，为何要这么设计，砍 USB3.0 总线有什么意义啊……","content_rendered":"<p>以前一直不明白，电视 /机顶盒厂商把 USB3.0 阉割成 2.0 ，千兆 LAN 阉割成百兆，能省几个钱。\n结果今天在雷鸟的论坛看到，其产品的 Wifi6 都仅支持 200Mbps ，有用户提到是联发科芯片的原因。\n遂前往联发科官网查询，发现如下：\n<a href=\"https://www.mediatek.cn/products/productSpecs/mt9632\" rel=\"nofollow\">MT9632</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://loli.tc/image/Qtyv\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://loli.tc/image/Qtyv</a></p>\n<p>仅 USB2.0 ，并因此导致走 usb 的网卡也仅能跑满 2.0 的速度。\n不明白所谓旗舰芯片，为何要这么设计，砍 USB3.0 总线有什么意义啊……</p>\n","last_modified":1639199888,"replies":19,"id":821500},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_large.png?m=1635654723","name":"bb","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_normal.png?m=1635654723","title":"宽带症候群","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/bb","topics":10037,"footer":"","header":"网速很重要。比快更快。","title_alternative":"Broadband Symptom Complex","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/a3c6/5c29/108_mini.png?m=1635654723","stars":5256,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":108,"parent_node_name":"geek"},"member":{"username":"atumu","website":null,"github":null,"psn":null,"avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b8592b04ded4b728026bef3f039971b9?s=24&d=retro","bio":null,"url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/atumu","tagline":null,"twitter":null,"created":1472384686,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b8592b04ded4b728026bef3f039971b9?s=24&d=retro","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/b8592b04ded4b728026bef3f039971b9?s=24&d=retro","location":null,"btc":null,"id":189159},"last_reply_by":"boris93","last_touched":1639221356,"title":"求救各位大佬, 端口映射不通","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/821521","created":1639208107,"deleted":0,"content":"北京联通,做了光猫桥接, 路由器用的华为荣耀 pro 2. \r\n\r\n我只想简单映射几个 web, 可是根据在 https://www.ip138.com/ 搜到的外网 ip + 路由器 NAT 映射的端口, 却总是访问不通,在 http://tool.chinaz.com/port/ 做端口扫描,也显示端口在关闭状态, 用花生壳也没成功,就这样 ipv4 不行, 又在阿里买了个域名配置了 ipv6 地址也无法访问(ipv6 地址在 https://www.test-ipv6.com/ 获取).日了狗了\r\n \r\n请各位大佬给点建议思路","content_rendered":"北京联通,做了光猫桥接, 路由器用的华为荣耀 pro 2. <br /><br />我只想简单映射几个 web, 可是根据在 <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.ip138.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://www.ip138.com/</a> 搜到的外网 ip + 路由器 NAT 映射的端口, 却总是访问不通,在 <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://tool.chinaz.com/port/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">http://tool.chinaz.com/port/</a> 做端口扫描,也显示端口在关闭状态, 用花生壳也没成功,就这样 ipv4 不行, 又在阿里买了个域名配置了 ipv6 地址也无法访问(ipv6 地址在 <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.test-ipv6.com/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\">https://www.test-ipv6.com/</a> 获取).日了狗了<br /> <br />请各位大佬给点建议思路","last_modified":1639208568,"replies":18,"id":821521},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913","name":"apple","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913","title":"Apple","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","topics":17169,"footer":"","header":"设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。","title_alternative":"Apple","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","stars":2031,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":184,"parent_node_name":"hardware"},"member":{"username":"daimon1","website":"","github":null,"psn":null,"avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5984/81d8/423564_mini.png?m=1635858363","bio":"","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/daimon1","tagline":"","twitter":null,"created":1561093589,"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5984/81d8/423564_mini.png?m=1635858363","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5984/81d8/423564_mini.png?m=1635858363","location":"","btc":null,"id":423564},